PROBLEM 2:
Finding the subarray with the largest sum from a integer array nums

variables: list of integers,the greatest sum of two integers.
Begin
function max_subarray_sum(nums):
    if nums is empty:
        return o
    initialize:
    global_max = nums[0]
    current_max = nums[0]
    iteration:
    for i from 1 to length(nums) -1:
        current_num = nums(i)
    update the global and current_max:
    current_max = Max(current_num,current_max + current_num)

    if current_max > global_max:
        global_max = current_max
    return global_max
End